	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just started programming in 6502 assembly yesterday as part of my course.
<br />
<br />I'm wondering what's needed, besides knowing the launguage, to create NES games? Do you guys create NES games from scratch, and do the games work on an emulator such as NESten?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
