		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Maca wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Do you guys create NES games from scratch</div>
<br />Define "scratch". Yes, we usually create completely original programs intended to run on NES, as opposed to "ROM hacking" that uses an existing commercial game's engine. But most of the playable stuff is based on an existing rule set.

		

